title: Home page
raw_template:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ page.title }}</title>
    {{ 'varbase.css' | stylesheet_tag }}
    {{ 'index.css' | stylesheet_tag }}
    {{ 'base.js' | javascript_tag }}
  </head>
  <body>
    {% section header %}
    
    {% block 'main' %}

      {% include cookies %}

      {% section 'hero' %}

      {% section 'about_us' %}

      {% section 'featured_products' %}

      {% section 'product_suggestion' %}

      {% include newsl %}
    
    {% endblock %}

  </body>

  {% section footer %}
</html>
